@startuml
title system_info — cache miss detailed sequence
actor User
participant Discord as "discord.py"
participant Bot as "DiscordBot"
participant AsyncRoute as "ed_route_async"
participant Route as "ed_route"
participant Cache as "Ed_Cache"
database DB as "TinyDB (data/*.db)"
participant EDGIS as "EDGIS API"

User -> Discord: `!system_info Sol`
Discord -> Bot: invoke system_info(ctx, "Sol")
Bot -> AsyncRoute: get_system_info("Sol")
AsyncRoute -> Route: get_system_info("Sol")
Route -> DB: open DB file
Route -> Cache: Ed_Cache(database)
Route -> Cache: find_system_info("Sol")
Cache -> DB: get_system("Sol")
DB --> Cache: null
Cache -> EDGIS: GET /coords?q=Sol
EDGIS --> Cache: { name: "Sol", coords: {x:..., y:..., z:...}, ... }
Cache -> DB: insert_system(system_info)
DB --> Cache: confirmation
Cache --> Route: return system_info
Route --> AsyncRoute: return system_info
AsyncRoute --> Bot: await resolves with system_info
Bot -> Discord: ctx.send("Sol: <system_info JSON>")
@enduml
